quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  46,1,"Haa, Miiym. (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwazo zose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  46,2,"Imanurwa ryiki gitabu gitagatifu ca Qur’aani ryavuye ku Mana, nyene ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  46,3,"Ntitwaremye aya Majuru n’Isi canke ibiri hagati yavyo atari uko vyose ari ivy’ukuri, kandi ku kiringo categekanijwe, n’abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri barirengagiza kubutumwa batuzwa"
  46,4,"N’uvuge uti:- mbega mubona gute bamwe musenga, n’ukureka Imana y’ukuri, ni munyereke ico baremye ngaha kw’Isi, canke barafise ishirahamwe ry’ibiri mu majuru? Ni munzanire igitabu camyeho imbere yiki, canke ikimenyetso icarico cose c’ubumenyi, ni mwaba muvugisha ukuri"
  46,5,"N’abazimiye bakuru nibande gusumba bamwe basaba abatari Imana y’ukuri, nabo batazo bishura kugeza k’umusi w’imperuka, kandi batazi n’ibisabisho vy’abo"
  46,6,"Mugihe bazokwegeranywa abantu bazoba ari abansi b’abandi, kandi bazohakana amasengesho y’abo"
  46,7,"Mugihe bazosomerwa amajambo yacu matagatifu ari kumugaragaro, bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri bazo vuga hejuru y’ukuri kuba shikira bati:- ubu n’uburozi buri k’umugaragaro"
  46,8,"Canke baka vuga bati:- niwe yavyi teguriye wenyene, vuga uti:- ni naba naravyi teguriye jewe, ntaco muzo mfasha imbere y’Imana, kuko niyo ifise ubumenyi bwivyo muriko muragira, kuko niyo ihagije kuba ariyo cabona hagati yanje na mwebwe, nayo niyo ifise ikigongwe n’impuhwe nyinshi zihagije"
  46,9,"Vuga uti:- jewe sindi igitangaro mu ntumwa z’Imana kandi nta bumenyi mfise bw’ingene nzogirwa, canke ingene muzogirwa mwebwe, ntakindi nkurikira atari ivyo neretswe kuri jewe, kandi nta nico narimwo atari ukuba ndi uwutuza gusa, kandi mbonekana k’umugaragaro"
  46,10,"Vuga uti:- mbega mubona gute iki gitabu nicaba kivuye ku Mana namwe mwagi hakanye n’ivyabona muri bene Israeri bari ivyabona k’uburorero bwibi, batako baremera ibi vyose, namwe mukagira amanyama, mu vy’ukuri Imana ntirongora abantu bahemukiye imitima yabo"